src_text: Uvuyiswano Ikhabhinethi ivakalisa ukuvuyisana kunye neminqweno emihle ku: UMongameli Ramaphosa ngokuwongwa ngesidanga sobugqirha i-Honoris Causa kwiYunivesithi yase-Cheikh Anta Diop e-Dakar, e-Senegal, ehlonitshwa njengenye yeeyunivesithi zase-Afrika ezibalaseleyo kwihlabath Kwiminyaka engamashumi amabini anesithoba eyadlulayo, owayesakuba nguMongameli uNelson Mandela wawongwa ngesidanga sobugqirha esifanayo ngexesha apho isizwe sethu sasingekakhululek
